**Novel Contributions:**

1. **Endogenous-visual-form codec with profile / symmetry / spatial-frequency / drift replay.** A deterministic codec in which a bounded internal geometric form is encoded and recovered with profile, symmetry, spatial-frequency, and drift properties preserved within the declared endogenous-visual-form scope. The bounded endogenous-visual-form replay surface — exact on the specific bounded object and explicitly scoped to endogenous visual-form geometry rather than broader cognitive content — is the novel contribution. Code: resolved via the Citation Index at the Master Resolver Endpoint (ZPE-Mental).

